{"tid":220901,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺d毒撚以為自己打扮下會溝到女好嘔心","createTime":"2017-04-28T09:56:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T17:21:35.000Z","uid":68626,"like":15,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"525d1fcfbd089e1dc306cb74e29b9dc4d552eb99","tid":220901,"uid":68626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T09:56:44.000Z","msg":"每次見到d毒撚 係到操大隻/著名牌/gel頭<br />\n我都覺得好撚可憐<br />\n其實佢地知唔知佢地既毒撚除係<br />\n由內而外咁散發出黎<br />\n唔係話打扮下可以補救到<br />\n有時d毒撚 唔帶眼鏡轉帶con<br />\n以為可以比人耳目一新既感覺<br />\n其實只係由四眼毒撚變兩眼毒撚<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b9e868f0db2afc5884cc571751d66eb3c4a253","tid":220901,"uid":104500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T09:59:36.000Z","msg":"我覺得連執正少少嘅心都無嘅毒撚會仲可悲啲"},{"pid":"7d1970e4eb66040f2f2073ad5c451753d8668694","tid":220901,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:03:19.000Z","msg":"其實依種毒撚肯為脫毒而努力係件好事, <br />\n每一樣少少既改變, 亦都會慢慢增加佢地既自信, 最終脫毒成功 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25080009160b863ff6347e6e849b3aedc13fc85b","tid":220901,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:03:46.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"8326504d397768f16374148ef109e9009d1e9fa0","tid":220901,"uid":31389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:05:24.000Z","msg":"你照下塊鏡啦<br />\n人地起碼識自己改變下<br />\n你呢就剩係識上網笑鳩人"},{"pid":"084c4f6e70456b7eb084cb5c115a10b19be5b9e3","tid":220901,"uid":68626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:06:44.000Z","msg":"樓主係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想直線引人鼓勵自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6022b43088ba7460c762f0f6944473b1e14b9461","tid":220901,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:07:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad